NOTE
----
Ding's autoloader has been renamed to the namespace Ding\Autoloader and the
class name is now \Ding\Autoloader\Autoloader so we now honor namespace to
filesystem convention for classes. Thus, change your code to:

require_once 'Ding/Autoloader/Autoloader.php'; // Include ding autoloader.
\Ding\Autoloader\Autoloader::register(); // Call autoloader register for ding autoloader.